column5: 1st Place Ben Ebeling & Emily Deeks 52.97 lbs $650.00 2nd Place Don Erskine & James Southward 38.40 lbs $455.00 3rd Place Steve Piggot & John Gsterino 37.96 lbs $195.00 Big Fish Calcutta Andrew Mc Evoy & Peter Hoffmann 17.30lbs $325.00 Thanks to everyone that showed up for the Big Crazy Cat Tourney again this year im happy everyone caught FISH see ya next Year Mr & Mrs Fishmaster

Thanks for hosting again Steve - it was lots of fun! Andrew and I just missed the overall weight payout (we finished 4th @ 36.4lbs) but took the big fish calcutta - gotta say it's pretty cool to get paid to go fishing!!!
Next year Pete  I did't beat you by much.LOL It was good to see you agian.
Likewise Steve! If we could have just culled that little one pounder we would have been in the money!!!

Glad to see you boys back again this year ,,,I will see what happens In Costa Rica all next winter and hopefully I will have time to run it for 2015 ...hard to leave chartering for Marlin and Sailfish to come back home
Nice to see a couple of OFCer's with a bit of extra cash in their pockets, congrats!!
